\qt@newcmd\qurantrans@en@mmcclviii{%
He said: O my Lord! in what wise shall there be for me a boy, whereas my wife hath been barren, and surely have reached an age of extreme degree?\qt@no{(8)}}%
\qt@newcmd\qurantrans@en@mmcclix{%
Allah said: even so! Thy Lord saith: it is unto Me easy, whereas surely I created thee afore when thou wast not aught.\qt@no{(9)}}%
\qt@newcmd\qurantrans@en@mmcclx{%
