Verily those who believe and do righteOUs works--anon the Compassionate shall appoint for them affection. *Chapter: 19\qt@no{(96)}}%
\qt@newcmd\qurantrans@en@mmcccxlvii{%
So We have made it easy in thine tongue in order that thou mayest thereby give glad tidings unto the Godfearing and warn thereby a people contentious. *Chapter: 19\qt@no{(97)}}%
\qt@newcmd\qurantrans@en@mmcccxlviii{%
