\qt@newcmd\qurantrans@en@mmcccli{%
But only as an admonition unto him who feareth. *Chapter: 20\qt@no{(3)}}%
\qt@newcmd\qurantrans@en@mmccclii{%
A down-sent from Him who Created the earth and the heavens high.\qt@no{(4)}}%
\qt@newcmd\qurantrans@en@mmcccliii{%
The Compassionate on the Throne is established.\qt@no{(5)}}%
