And I! I have chosen thee hearken thou then to that which shall be revealed.\qt@no{(13)}}%
\qt@newcmd\qurantrans@en@mmccclxii{%
Verily I! I am Allah! no God there is butI; so Worship Me, and establish prayer for My remembrance.\qt@no{(14)}}%
\qt@newcmd\qurantrans@en@mmccclxiii{%
Verily the Hour is coming--I wish to conceal it - in Order that every one may be requited according to that which he hath endeavoured.\qt@no{(15)}}%
\qt@newcmd\qurantrans@en@mmccclxiv{%
So let not him who believeth not therein and followeth his own desire keep thee away therefrom lest thou perish.\qt@no{(16)}}%
\qt@newcmd\qurantrans@en@mmccclxv{%
And what is that in thy right hand, O Musa!\qt@no{(17)}}%
\qt@newcmd\qurantrans@en@mmccclxvi{%
